Package: ggjbrowse
Title: ggplot2 Geoms and Data Access for Genomic Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("JBrowse", "Team", , "jbrowse@gmod.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides ggplot2 geoms and scales for creating JBrowse-style genomic
    visualizations, along with data access functions for genomic file formats.
    Includes geoms for gene tracks, coverage plots, variant displays, and
    multi-track assemblies. Supports BigWig, VCF, GFF3, BAM, and BED formats
    through a unified interface for reproducible genomic analysis.
